{"tid":2169303,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】張沛樂曬性感內衣相分享美胸秘訣　網民：咁惹火得唔得？","createTime":"2020-08-22T11:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T13:00:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"34a2ed00feb9e98a705837c382317fb4f3b3aa11","tid":2169303,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"「宅男女神」張沛樂（沙津）曾參加ViuTV選美節目《美選D.n.A》，卻於決賽八強止步，但她仍憑玲瓏浮突的好身材闖出名堂，18年更與好友趙詠瑤出版「旅遊書」《閨蜜遊記》。張沛樂人氣不俗，憑一己之力在IG累積逾16萬粉絲，昨日（21/8）她就貼出穿着內衣的性感照片，姣好身材一覽無遺，她又分享了美胸秘訣：「作為女人最重要就係揀啱一個戴得舒服、貼身又有承托力嘅Bra，先可以令自己嘅胸部保持堅挺！」網民紛紛留下心心眼Emoji，當中更有留言謂：「咁惹火得唔得㗎？」"},{"pid":"9931ca3a137d45887ac3140a38cbacbd7ddd588f","tid":2169303,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200821/373590893602672640.jpeg/sbf3eI-j5I_D36tgS5N5lHND4OIzKXv5-1N3b_tTd28?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200821%2F373590893602672640.jpeg%2Fsbf3eI-j5I_D36tgS5N5lHND4OIzKXv5-1N3b_tTd28%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1cf33e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200821/373590895343308800.jpeg/Gio7CrjL8rkXvWRffhDCLNQP6N5sn5x5vtEPUb7RD1E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200821%2F373590895343308800.jpeg%2FGio7CrjL8rkXvWRffhDCLNQP6N5sn5x5vtEPUb7RD1E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2f3deec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200821/373590899919294464.jpeg/m3lf4Jg1yyv_g9dES1bHa6Mq5X0kUQLbwURBFsFEQRY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200821%2F373590899919294464.jpeg%2Fm3lf4Jg1yyv_g9dES1bHa6Mq5X0kUQLbwURBFsFEQRY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=605de67b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200714/359653613787811840.jpeg/mlXAYSJz77m9V4wLWWnr-E4KEwV4m